Mon Aug 22 16:39:49-0500 2012                       Matias A Cabral (macabral)

Add of first version of files for wwinit ICR and OFED options. The OFED target
builds, install and performs a basic configuration the Open Fabric Alliance
(http://www.openfabrics.org) InfiniBand support package. The ICR target
performs several steps to help during the installation of cluster to have an
Intel(R) Cluster Ready (http://software.intel.com/en-us/cluster-ready)
compliant cluster. See icr/AUTHORS. 
